headline: Lockheed Martin Expands Autonomy And Missile Defense Capacity As Orders Build
summary: Lockheed Martin (NYSE:LMT) has introduced its Lamprey Multi-Mission Autonomous Undersea Vehicle, expanding its unmanned naval systems offering. The company has signed a framework agreement that targets a fourfold increase in THAAD missile interceptor production. Lockheed Martin is breaking ground on a new advanced manufacturing site, the Munitions Acceleration Center, to support higher output.
